code: import Config from"../Config";export default async function CheckJWTaccess(access_token){try{const response=await fetch(Config.API_URL+"auth/users/",{method:'GET',headers:{'Authorization':"JWT ".concat(access_token),'Content-Type':'application/json'}});if(response.ok){console.log("JWT access token is valid");return true;}if(!response.ok){const data=await response.json();throw new Error(JSON.stringify(data));}}catch(error){console.log("JWT access token is invalid");console.log(error);return false;}}
